text.tspan: To add a model diagram create an image with a height to width ratio of 2
name it system.png and overwrite the default value. If you do not want a
a model diagram or just want to get rid of this message then delete the file
system.png that came with the template.
You can use the file library/templates/system.svg as a starting point for
creating a model diagram. This template was created in inkscape
